INSERT INTO wp_posts VALUES('247', '1', '2012-08-17 19:49:47', '2012-08-17 19:49:47', '<em>From day one babies can distinguish light, shapes and patterns, not to mention that they love to look at faces. Vision is just one of the staggering number of concerns a new parent has for the new addition to their family. </em>\n\nIt is extremely important to keep a newborn’s eyes clean and healthy. Use a damp washcloth to wipe clean the eyes form the inside to the outside corners. Remember to be gentle and use warm, not hot, water. Wash your hands before you begin and use a different portion of the cloth for each pass to avoid infection.\n\nAnother of the many concerns with newborns is when their eyes “wander” and have difficulty focusing. If your child has a family history of lazy or crossed eyes you might want to have them examined, however, it is common for the first few months until the child develops proper eye co-ordination. Although always trust your instinct, if you ever have any major concerns take your child to your health-care provider.', 'Babies & Toddlers', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '203-autosave', '', '', '2012-08-17 19:49:47', '2012-08-17 19:49:47', '', '203', 'http://agdev.ca/crystalvision/?p=247', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO wp_posts VALUES('205', '1', '2012-07-27 17:15:14', '2012-07-27 17:15:14', '<em>Eye tests can be done on children of any age, even if they are not talking yet. Some symptoms that might warrant a doctor’s appointment include:</em>\r\n<div class=\"columns\">\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Blurred vision</li>\r\n	<li>Headaches</li>\r\n	<li>Red, itchy or watery eyes</li>\r\n	<li>Squinting, rubbing the eyes, or excessive blinking</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Covering or closing one eye</li>\r\n	<li>Holding objects too close</li>\r\n	<li>Reading items or watching television very closely</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<hr class=\"clr\" />\r\nChildren rarely know that they have a vision problem. As with most vision ailments, changes happen very slowly and the child may even think that all people see the same way as them, so they have no idea that there is something wrong.\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Children', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'children', '', '', '2012-08-17 19:53:37', '2012-08-17 19:53:37', '', '60', 'http://agdev.ca/crystalvision/?page_id=205', '0', 'page', '', '0');
